evStoryDefThreat1 = "You have to realize that adventures are not always as rosy as some stories make them out to be. The hardships take their toll on you and your party.",
evStoryDefThreat2 = "You sense a dark force against you, fueling your enemies into furious attacks",
evStoryMirrormere = "Durin I once looked into the mirror lake and in broad daylight saw his head surrounded by stars. He then founded the dwarven kingdom of Khazad-dûm. Durin's crown is said to have been modeled after this sight. Today, Durin's stone commemorates this legend, although its tip is broken and the runic inscription within is weathered.",
evStrongEnemy = "Powerful Enemy",
